                [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasSubsection [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                    oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                    oc:codeContent """public Map<String, Object> getUserWithErrorHandling(String userId) {
    return restClient.get()
        .uri("/users/{id}", userId)
        .retrieve()
        .onStatus(HttpStatusCode::is4xxClientError, (request, response) -> {
            throw new UserNotFoundException("User not found: " + userId);
        })
        .onStatus(HttpStatusCode::is5xxServerError, (request, response) -> {
            throw new ExternalServiceException("External service error");
        })
        .body(new ParameterizedTypeReference<Map<String, Object>>() {});
}
""" ;
