                [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                            oc:textContent "Spring Framework 6.1 (Spring Boot 3.2+) introduces `RestClient`, a modern, fluent API for synchronous HTTP requests that replaces the older `RestTemplate`. While `RestTemplate` still works, `RestClient` is the recommended approach for new code." ] ;
                    oc:sectionLevel 2 ;
                    oc:sectionOrder 1 ;
                    oc:sectionTitle "Overview" ],
                [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                            oc:codeContent """// WebClient for reactive/async operations
WebClient webClient = WebClient.create(baseUrl);

Mono<User> userMono = webClient.get()
    .uri("/users/{id}", userId)
    .retrieve()
    .bodyToMono(User.class);
""" ;
